A Thousand Splendid Suns is a 2007 novel by Afghan - American author Khaled Hosseini , his second , following his bestselling debut , The Kite Runner ( 2003 ) . The book was released on May 22 , 2007 , and has received favorable prepublication reviews from Kirkus , Publishers Weekly , Library Journal , and Booklist , as well as reaching # 2 on Amazon.com 's bestseller list before its release . Kirkus Reviews ( March 1 , 2007 ) . Publishers Weekly ( February 23 , 2007 ) . Library Journal ( review archived at MARINet ) ( January 2007 ) . 